User Stories

User will visit welcome and enter their own profile - the names of the wedding parties, wedding date ..
User will be able to Create an invited guests list/data base
User will be able to Add Guests - including mailing, email, spouse information
User will be able to Read Guests
User will be able to Update Guests
User will be able to Delete Guests
User will be able to enter place card information for Guests

Bronze
User will create edit delete Guest list
User will  create edit delete Place Cards

Silver
User will be able to enter information about the wedding

Gold
Improve on above with look and functionality - including program intuition
